; Coverage test for item.cc lookup switch break statements.
; Exercises branches for function name prefixes 'b' (L426), 'e' (L449),
; 'f' (L458), 'i' (L472), 'n' (L482), 's' (L498), 'v' (L515).
; Accessing parent.X calls xact_t::lookup which falls through to
; item_t::lookup for most names.

2024/01/01 * Test
    ; Payee: vendor
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(parent.beg_line)|%(parent.end_line)|%(parent.seq)|%(parent.id)|%(parent.status)|%(account)\n"
7|10|1|1|1|Expenses:Food
7|10|1|1|1|Assets:Cash
end test
